14. Be2
14. Qxf6
15. Qxd5+
15. Kc8 {White finds themselves in a challenging situation. The main problem is that White cannot castle, as that would leave the bishop on e2 unprotected, and also the pawns on b2 and c2 are currently vulnerable.} 
