16. Qd6 {Looks totally fine for Black. The machine will tell you it's equal, but please give me Black here. At least from a practical point of view, I don't like White's position (what is the plan?), while I see plenty of knight jumps coming up very soon.16...Ne4?!backfires, because of17.Bd4!±followed by f2-f3.} 
