19. Qxb2 {This is now possible with a sharp game. An important idea is that White can't simply just invade on b7.} 
20. Rab1
20. Qxc2
21. Rxb7 {And now we can see why!} 
21. Rxg3+
22. hxg3
22. Qxh7 {Wins the queen and the game.} 
