11. h5 {A great idea, which prevents g2-g4 and offers Black a solid blockade on the light squares.   The bishop on c1 can't be activated by means of f4-f5 anytime soon. In the game Morovic-Hansen, Wijk aan Zee 1994, Black was in good shape. Apart from the standard plans based on either ...c6-c5 and/or ...Nb6-d5, there is now also additional ideas on the kingside with ...Ng4 or ...h5-h4.   As the situation in the centre is under control, Black is not in a rush to castle kingside.} 
