12. bxc5
12. Bxc5
13. Be1 {13.dxc5?Qxc5+followed by taking on c4 when Black is pawn up.} 
13. Be7 {With a perfectly fine position for Black, as very soon the rooks will start exerting pressure along the half-open files.} 
