17. Bb3
17. c5 {Threatening either to take or ...c5-c4.} 
18. dxc5
18. Qc6
19. O-O
19. Qxc5+
20. Kh1
20. Rbc8 {Followed by ...Rxd2 and take on c3 the material balance will be restored again with a more or less equal endgame in prospect.} 
