6. Nf3 {Frankly, it does seem a bit weird voluntarily placing the knight in a pin and therefore I think we should try to punish it with active play against the pawn on d4.} 
6. Nc6 {Preparing to castle queenside. White has to be extremely careful not to lose the d-pawn without a fight.} 
7. h3 {Resolving the problem of the pinned knight is the best White can do.} 
 {In case you are looking for a simpler way of obtaining full equality I can also recommend:} 7. Bxf3
