9. bxa6 {In a way, of course, it's a pity having the pawn formation on the queenside. However, on the positive side, Black can be relieved that they have eliminated White's light-squared bishop. The plan here is to continue with ...f7-f6 and ...e7-e5, solidifying Black's advantage without a doubt.} 
