10. Nbd7 {The downside of White's early Ne5 that White can hardly avoid any exchanges, as going back to f3 is basically admitting things have gone wrong.} 
11. Nxg6
11. hxg6 {Black is still rock-solid and White is unable breaking through the barricades.} 
12. Rae1 {Bringing the final piece to the party.} 
12. Nb6 {Tempo!} 
13. Bb3
13. c5 {Even before deciding which side to castle, Black is able to free the position and makes use of the potential queen trade on the d-file.} 
